import React from "react";

function LogIn(props) {
  return (
    <form className="m-12 mt-32 text-center px-12 py-16 border-[1px] ">
      <label htmlFor="" className="block">
        Sign In
      </label>

      <label htmlFor="username" className="block mt-8">
        Username
      </label>
      <input
        type="text"
        name="username"
        id="username"
        className="w-full border-[1px] mt-4"
      />

      <label htmlFor="password" className="block mt-8">
        password
      </label>
      <input
        type="password"
        name="password"
        id="password"
        className="w-full border-[1px] mt-4"
      />
    </form>
  );
}

export default LogIn;
